reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This bag has a pocket for everything! I can carry two 17 inch laptops in the back pocket for both of my job roles. There are two larger pockets in the center for separating folders and a couple of smaller ones for other items (mouse, post-its, etc.). The front has room at the bottom for lots (below the pens and other items demonstrated). I put my charger in the outer most front so that I'm always prepared. The best part is that it feels great on - when to capacity, I don't notice the weight. It's a good, strong material and sleek - there are many pockets, but it doesn't look busy. I consider it my mobile office and love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality and Very Useful
reviews.reviewText: I have not expected the backpack to be such good quality at so reasonable price. The fabric and sewing are both good quality. The backpack looks clean and neat. It has enough room to hold laptop, books, folders, etc. I expect the backpack will last for many years.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Returned It, BUT, it was as described
reviews.reviewText: The bag came exactly as described. I love the many different compartments and pockets that it had, it can help you carry lots of different things in it without having to worry. The only downside for me was the fabric material. I was really hoping for something with premium quality fabric but that was not the case, it felt a little cheap to me unfortunately and it was a little rough on the skin to carry even with hands. That was something that I cannot judge by pictures until I had to try it first-hand. Also, I noticed that the back side of the bag was not well-tailored, there were some spaces through the bag and I was seriously worried that it won't last for too long or maybe would not handle heavy and large-sized items.On the other hand, the bag is a really good option for many college/school student and business-oriented people if you are looking for something that is not expensive and would just do the job for you.I later happened to go for a little more expensive option that had really good quality material and I personally would not regret that, I feel like this is an investment towards my future to have a secure bag that I will know to last for a good while.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Spacious lots of compartments but one tore 8 months in
reviews.reviewText: Great space and pockets and compartments - but 7-8 months using it and the material around the zipper of the second biggest compartment has started to tear. So indicates that likely isn’t the best quality. Also the zippers of that compartment (middle and second largest) have frequently gotten a bit stuck in one direction but I worked around it just zipping the other direction (but it was an indication of lesser quality of a zipper).

reviews.reviewText: Purchased for my bf for Christmas. He usually travels with a lot of equipment, a laptop, clothes, miscellaneous items. He's been really happy with the durability and the functionality of the bag. BUY THIS BAG!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Secure and Convenient
reviews.reviewText: The Monsdle Travel Laptop Backpack is an exceptional choice for travelers who prioritize security, convenience, and comfort. With its anti-theft design and USB charging port, this backpack offers practical features that make it stand out in the market.One of the standout features of the Monsdle Travel Laptop Backpack is its anti-theft design. The hidden zippers and multiple layers of protection ensure that your belongings remain safe and secure, even in crowded areas. The main compartment is cleverly positioned against the back, adding an extra layer of security and deterring potential pickpockets. This feature provides peace of mind, particularly when traveling to unfamiliar destinations.The built-in USB charging port is a game-changer for modern travelers. With this convenient feature, you can easily charge your devices on the go, eliminating the need to search for a power outlet. The backpack is equipped with a built-in charging cable, allowing you to connect your power bank and keep your devices powered and accessible throughout your journey.In terms of storage, the Monsdle Travel Laptop Backpack offers ample space for all your essentials. It features dedicated compartments for laptops, tablets, and other belongings, as well as multiple organization pockets and sleeves to keep everything tidy and easily accessible. Whether you're carrying your laptop for work or packing for a weekend getaway, this backpack provides the storage you need.Comfort is not compromised with the Monsdle Travel Laptop Backpack. The adjustable and padded shoulder straps ensure a comfortable fit, reducing strain on your shoulders and back even during extended periods of wear. The breathable material on the back panel enhances airflow, keeping you cool and comfortable throughout your travels.
